OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRisk of rain in far eastern
OL,6,Fcoastal areas, otherwise a bright and
OL,7,Fchilly start. Cloud increasing,
OL,8,Fleaving sunny spells and showers,
OL,9,Flocally heavy, with the risk of hail
OL,10,Fand thunder, during the afternoon.
OL,11,FLighter winds than Sunday. Feeling
OL,12,Fwarmer.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FEarly evening showers fading
OL,15,Fto leave a dry night, with prolonged
OL,16,Fclear spells. Turning chilly, with a
OL,17,Ftouch of frost in prone rural spots.
OL,18,FSome isolated mist and fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
